<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich I. von Hohenzollern, Markgraf von Brandenburg und Burggraf von Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt seine Gesandtschaft zum Gerichtstag vor dem Adressaten mit Heinrich X. von Plauen am Montag vor Fronleichnam zu Bayreuth an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_449" id="223v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_449_r1l10"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l11">vnd <expan>Burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu Nuremberg etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_449_r1l12"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Vns haben <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ~ freẅnde dıe bey <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l13">ʒu Peyrreẅt yecʒ geweſen ſeyn . <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıngen geſagt / wıe der <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l14">von plawen . mıt Jn reden laſſen vnd auch ſelbs geredt hab . auf ſölıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l15"><expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> / daʒ er eins <expan>fürkome<ex>n</ex>s</expan> mıt vns für eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> / auf den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l17">montag vor <expan>Corp<ex>or</ex>ıs</expan> xpı ſchıerıſt gen peyrreẅt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_449_r1l16">hab </ab></add> begert vnd ſıe das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l18"><expan>angebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd daʒ wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> in kürcʒ ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> tun ſölten ob wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l19">das tun wölten . Alſo tun wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l20">auf den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> tag <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / gen <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Plawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l21">für eẅr <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> ſchıken <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> . Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l22"><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ / daʒ eẅr gnade beſtellen welle . daʒ das ~ dem von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l23">Plawen alſo ʒu <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> getan <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . / Vnd ob darein ıcht fıele daʒ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l24">von plawen ʒu dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> tag niht <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt / oder des vns ſuſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l25">ein notdruft <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu wıſſen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . Daʒ vns das eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒeıt = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_line_1577284501998_8659">lıch beuor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künden</expan> laſſe . als etc Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_line_1577284504918_8664"><expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_449_r1l30"><expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>feſtu<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Penthecoſt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_449" id="223v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                            <expan>burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Nuremberg etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns haben <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        frewnde, die bey <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu Peyrrewt yecz gewesen seyn,
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dingen gesagt, wie der
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von Plawen mit in reden lassen und auch
                        selbs geredt hab auf sölich <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, daz er eins
                                <expan>fürkome<ex>n</ex>s</expan> mit uns für ewr
                        <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> auf den <app><note><q type="date">montag vor
                            <expan>corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> Christi schierist</q>08.06.1422</note></app> gen Peyrrewt
                            <add>hab</add> begert, und sie das <expan>angebotte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und daz wir <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> in kürcz ein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> tun sölten, ob wir das tun wölten.
                        Also tun wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                        auf den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> tag
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> erber <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
                        gen <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Plawen für ewr
                                <expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> schiken
                                <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan> und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz ewr gnade
                        bestellen welle, daz das dem von Plawen also zu
                            <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> getan <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und,
                        ob darein icht fiele, daz der von Plawen zu dem
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> tag niht <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wölt oder des uns sust ein notdruft <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu wissen
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, daz uns das ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zeitlich bevor
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künden</expan> lasse. Als etc. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>festu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>penthecost<ex>en</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
